description: Beautiful single family row house with garage parking, two bedrooms and one and a half bathrooms over three levels of living space. Pull into your private garage and head upstairs into a large eat-in kitchen and spacious living room with bay window. Kitchen features abundant cabinet space and sliding doors that open to a private rear deck. Upstairs you will find two king-sized bedrooms with ample closet space and a full bathroom. Hardwood floors, crown molding, laundry room, and ample storage space complete this wonderful home. Walk to the beach or dog park. This is a commuter's dream location 1 block from the Redline and Longwood buses.
